# Feature modules

```
features/<modulo>/
  types.ts, api.ts, labels.ts, hooks/, pages/
```

## api.ts

```ts
import { getJson, postJson, patchJson } from "@/shared/api/client"
import type { PaginatedResponse } from "@/shared/types/pagination"
```

Rutas y payloads deben coincidir con el API Python — ver `docs/API.md`.

